These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-1::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: orange, grey, light-blue, brown, fuchsia, azure, mauve
1. the person who likes fuchsia is between the person who likes light-blue and the person who likes grey##2
2. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
3. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
4. the person who likes azure is in the middle##1
5. the person who likes grey is in an odd position##4
6. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
7. the person who likes orange is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3     |    4    |   5    |    6     |    7     |
| Color   | brown | mauve | orange | azure | light-blue | fuchsia | grey |

