.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-2::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, havana, bolivar, prince, tiparillo, siglo, oliveros
1. the prince-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the havana-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
4. the bolivar-smoker is in an even position##4
5. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
6. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the montecristo-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2     |   3    |    4     |    5    |  6   |     7      |
| Cigar   | tiparillo | montecristo | siglo | havana | prince | bolivar | oliveros |

