.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-3::.
There 7 different types of food: cabbage, radish, potato, orange, pomegranate, carrot, garlic
1. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
2. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
3. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person eating garlic##3
5. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
6. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
7. the person eating potato is in an even position##4
8. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |   2   |      3      |         4          |      5       |     6     |    7    |
| Food   | radish | orange | cabbage | pomegranate | garlic | potato | carrot |

