.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-4::.
7 different games are played: chess, billiard, domino, backgammon, mah-jongg, whist, go
1. the person playing chess is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
3. the person playing domino is in an even position##4
4. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
5. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing chess##1
6. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
7. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
8. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3     |    4     |   5    |     6      |  7   |
| Game   | chess | go | backgammon | whist | mah-jongg | domino | billiard |

