.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-5::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, tram, van, boat, subway, airplane, motorbike
1. the person driving the van is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
6. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |  2   |    3    |    4     |   5   |   6   |   7    |
| Transport   | tram | boat | subway | van | bike | motorbike | airplane |

