.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-6::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: collecting, chess, dancing, fishing, traveling, camping, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is in the middle##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |      2       |     3      |     4      |    5    |     6      |     7      |
| Hobby   | fishing | traveling | camping | collecting | dancing | chess | rock-climbing |

