.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-7::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: funk, metal, reggae, salsa, pop, classical, blues
1. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of funk##1
2. the fan of classical is in the middle##1
3. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of pop##1
4. the fan of salsa is the fan of salsa##1
5. the fan of blues is between the fan of reggae and the fan of classical##2
6. the fan of blues is in an odd position##4
7. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2    |    3     |  4  |   5   |    6     |   7    |
| Music-Genre   | funk | salsa | pop | classical | blues | reggae | metal |

