3. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the van##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
6. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
7. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the van##1
8. the person driving the tram is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |   2    |   3    |     4     |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Transport   | subway | ship | trike | boat | van | tram | roller |

