.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-17::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: july, april, november, october, december, september, may
1. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in july##2
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is in an even position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in november##2
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
6. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3     |    4     |    5    |     6     |   7   |
| Birthday   | september | december | july | october | may | april | november |

