.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-20::.
There 7 different types of food: broccoli, cucumber, zucchini, avocado, strawberry, grapes, pumpkin
 1. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
 2. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
 3. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
 4. the person eating strawberry is in an odd position##4
 5. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person eating pumpkin##3
 6. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
 7. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3
 8. the person eating grapes is in an odd position##4
 9. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
10. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |  2   |  3   |  4   |     5      |     6     |  7   |
| Food   | cucumber | broccoli | pumpkin | avocado | strawberry | zucchini | grapes |

 